
CLEAR_LINE(2)              silmul_efun             CLEAR_LINE(2)

名稱
     clear_line - 清除游標所在行

語法
     string clear_line ();

描述
     If  this_player()  has  the  "vt100"  attribute  set,   this
     simul_efun   will  return  the  VT100  "line  clear"  escape
     sequence, so that the string will clear the current line  on
     a VT100-compatible terminal.  If "vt100" is not set, returns
     a null string.

     注意:  Do NOT use ed to edit the file vt100.c, or the escape
     sequences  will be corrupted.  (ed strips out escape charac-
     ters).

相關命令
     inverse, blink,  bold,  underscore,  clear_screen,  up_line,
     erase_line

作者
     Ichabod@TMI, 3/19/93
     wade@future 4/7/1996 翻譯

MudOS Release 0.9         Last change:                   3-19-93

